<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/9982226-dealulcudor"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1338794473i/9982226._UY100_CR12,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/9982226-dealulcudor">Dealulcudor</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">There are instances of magical realism in this book. However, they are not as thoroughly exploited as in Ana Castillo&apos;s So Far from God, for instance.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">There are instances of magical realism in this book. However, they are not as thoroughly exploited as in Ana Castillo's So Far from God, for instance. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
