<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1409976-was-this-work-written-in-english-or">Was this work written in English or Spanish originally?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1409976'><a id="like_count_community_question_1409976" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1409976?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F41021622-dreaming-in-cuban">like</a></span>

