<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1409976-was-this-work-written-in-english-or">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1409976-was-this-work-written-in-english-or">Add your answer</a>
</li>
