<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/11589340-olivia"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1572041629i/11589340._UX100_CR0,38,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/11589340-olivia">Olivia</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
The author originally wanted to write it in Spanish but she decided that the story (at least for the original edition) would flow better in English.
</span>
</div>
