  <span id="freeText11043595050456661050" style="display:none">Oh, this makes the... what? 10th time now? Granted, I teach this book in one of my classes, else I probably would not have read it as often, but each time I honestly do find new points to discuss with students. More importantly, the students always bring up amazing points that have never occurred to me!<br />It does get better each time. If I could bump my rating up a half star, I'd do so.</span>
